						<summary>

						<p>The inscription is simply dated in the cyclic year Raudra. It records the gift of a house and 300 <hi rend="italic">kuḻi</hi> of land to a stone mason by name Maṇḍalam son of Māḍappiḷḷai (residing) in the <hi rend="italic">maḍaiviḷāgam</hi> of the temple by the deity (Nāyiṉār).</p>						

